   TripAdvisor

Guest's Voice

   We loved everything about this place.The staff were friendly and
   couldn't do enough to help in any way.The view from our spacious room
   was stunning overlooking the rice fields and at night you could see
   fireflies! A member of staff came to the room every evening to put the
   mozzy net around the bed and give it a quick spray which I thought was
   a nice touch. We also had a 15 min complimentary massage and afternoon
   tea. Would defiantly recommend.
   Amazing

   Lisa J
   Spacious rooms and nice views. If you miss the shuttle bus to ubud, you
   can hardly call uber or meter taxi. Rooms are not well sealed. Some
   insects can entrr sometimes. The geckos, frogs, and birds sounds are
   sometimes too loud inside the room at night. The first night was a bit
   annoying but got used to it later
   Great place with big room for improvement.

   M_R_Shafie
   We had 4 nights at this beautiful hotel. our room was amazing,
   overlooking the pool and rice terraces. The staff were brilliant and
   could not do enough for us. would recommend this hotel to anyone
   visiting Ubud and I would definitely stay there again.
   Amazing Hotel

   Debbie T
